---
const src = "/screenshots/open-superforecaster-architecture.png"
---

<figure class="architecture-shell fs-panel">
  <div class="architecture-scroll">
    <img
      class="architecture-slide"
      src={src}
      alt="Open Superforecaster architecture: a question fans out to parallel agents, source research and synthesis produce a probability and artifacts, while traces, benchmarks, and a local store form the trust chain"
      width="1672"
      height="941"
      loading="lazy"
      decoding="async"
    />
  </div>
  <figcaption class="architecture-caption">
    <span>Input → agent fan-out → source research → synthesis → probability → artifacts, all backed by traces, benchmarks, and a local store.</span>
    <a class="architecture-fullres" href={src} target="_blank" rel="noopener">View full resolution ↗</a>
  </figcaption>
</figure>
